WEBVTT

00:00:00.010 --> 00:00:25.890
Subtitle Provide by dramacool.asia Translator [Admin.@YNG]

00:00:30.210 --> 00:00:34.890
[Echoes of the Self]

00:00:39.320 --> 00:00:40.360
Your mother

00:00:40.360 --> 00:00:42.830
will never be honored
in the ancestral hall of Zhou's Mansion.

00:00:42.830 --> 00:00:42.920
Who says my aunt wanted to be honored
in the ancestral hall of Zhou's Mansion?

00:00:42.920 --> 00:00:44.660
[Deep Roots; Lush Branches]

00:00:46.250 --> 00:00:47.050
Move aside.

00:00:56.720 --> 00:00:57.710
My aunt

00:00:57.820 --> 00:00:59.750
is the Empress of Daqing's sister.

00:00:59.940 --> 00:01:00.900
After her death,

00:01:01.290 --> 00:01:03.410
her coffin should be returned to Daqing

00:01:03.410 --> 00:01:04.569
for a grand funeral.

00:01:05.040 --> 00:01:05.920
But...

00:01:06.330 --> 00:01:08.300
Madam Wang
was still a member of the Zhou family.

00:01:08.300 --> 00:01:10.100
Even if she can't be honored
in the ancestral hall,

00:01:10.100 --> 00:01:13.230
she should still be buried
in her husband's family tomb.

00:01:22.210 --> 00:01:24.030
Sharing a bed in life and a grave in death

00:01:24.030 --> 00:01:25.590
refers to loving couples.

00:01:25.890 --> 00:01:26.770
But now,

00:01:27.330 --> 00:01:28.650
does Uncle Kui have

00:01:29.590 --> 00:01:32.190
even the slightest affection
left for my aunt?

00:01:34.780 --> 00:01:36.020
Your Highness.

00:01:36.950 --> 00:01:39.680
Madam Wang
was a concubine in our Zhou's Mansion.

00:01:39.860 --> 00:01:41.680
This should be our responsibility...

00:01:41.680 --> 00:01:45.479
Uncle Kui, if you disagree,
then dissolve the nominal bond with her.

00:01:45.840 --> 00:01:47.560
As long as Xi agrees,

00:01:47.680 --> 00:01:48.539
my aunt

00:01:48.830 --> 00:01:50.759
will no longer
be part of the Zhou's Mansion

00:01:50.759 --> 00:01:52.690
and won't have to follow its rules.

00:01:59.240 --> 00:02:02.040
Your Highness,
since this is your kind intention,

00:02:02.240 --> 00:02:04.240
the master certainly won't refuse.

00:02:04.690 --> 00:02:05.600
After all,

00:02:05.650 --> 00:02:08.250
being buried
as the Empress of Daqing's sister

00:02:08.419 --> 00:02:10.840
would certainly be more prestigious
than the current arrangement.

00:02:10.840 --> 00:02:11.760
In three days,

00:02:11.810 --> 00:02:13.420
I will send people

00:02:13.650 --> 00:02:15.030
to take my aunt's coffin

00:02:15.580 --> 00:02:17.020
back to Daqing.

00:02:21.980 --> 00:02:23.290
Mother is already dead.

00:02:23.290 --> 00:02:24.420
In my previous life,

00:02:24.420 --> 00:02:26.370
I went down a path of no return.

00:02:26.800 --> 00:02:27.680
In this life,

00:02:28.700 --> 00:02:31.750
I hope you, Xi,
can live a pure and good life.

00:02:32.240 --> 00:02:33.570
As for everything else,

00:02:34.270 --> 00:02:35.380
leave it to me.

00:03:07.290 --> 00:03:09.610
That medicine was given by His Highness.

00:03:09.830 --> 00:03:11.110
Since it comes from

00:03:11.520 --> 00:03:12.760
the palace,

00:03:12.780 --> 00:03:14.420
Xi should recover faster.

00:03:15.340 --> 00:03:18.070
I've also asked the servants
to prepare some medicinal soup.

00:03:18.070 --> 00:03:19.470
After such a beating,

00:03:19.860 --> 00:03:21.860
her body will need careful tending.

00:03:22.500 --> 00:03:23.690
Miss Ruoyao.

00:03:24.990 --> 00:03:26.920
You really care about your sister.

00:03:28.340 --> 00:03:30.740
Your Highness must have heard some gossip,

00:03:30.840 --> 00:03:32.740
thinking that the Zhou family's true-born
and concubine-born daughters

00:03:32.740 --> 00:03:34.140
have always been at odds.

00:03:34.510 --> 00:03:35.710
Is it just gossip?

00:03:37.440 --> 00:03:39.160
She's my only sister.

00:03:39.410 --> 00:03:41.070
How could I not treat her well?

00:03:41.850 --> 00:03:43.700
It is only that birth sets us apart.

00:03:43.700 --> 00:03:45.360
My mother runs the household.

00:03:46.160 --> 00:03:47.680
If I were too close to Xi,

00:03:48.260 --> 00:03:50.160
the suffering she would endure

00:03:50.620 --> 00:03:52.680
would be ten or a hundred times worse.

00:03:53.140 --> 00:03:55.340
So I've misunderstood Ruoyao all along.

00:03:55.340 --> 00:03:57.390
And to marry the Crown Prince,

00:03:57.640 --> 00:04:00.900
I brought about her disfigurement
and her tragic suicide.

00:04:01.440 --> 00:04:02.510
Ruoyao.

00:04:02.820 --> 00:04:04.870
What Your Highness said
in the hall yesterday

00:04:04.870 --> 00:04:06.070
was excellent.

00:04:07.040 --> 00:04:08.760
Who says that after a woman dies,

00:04:08.760 --> 00:04:11.420
she must be buried
in her husband's family tomb?

00:04:11.600 --> 00:04:12.490
I think

00:04:12.920 --> 00:04:14.280
that after a woman dies,

00:04:14.610 --> 00:04:16.000
people tend to remember her

00:04:16.000 --> 00:04:17.260
only as someone's wife

00:04:17.260 --> 00:04:18.579
or mother,

00:04:18.959 --> 00:04:20.279
rather than recall

00:04:20.740 --> 00:04:21.959
her true name,

00:04:23.360 --> 00:04:25.560
what she accomplished,

00:04:26.320 --> 00:04:28.050
or the contributions she made.

00:04:28.610 --> 00:04:29.660
I believe

00:04:30.040 --> 00:04:31.500
that regardless of status

00:04:31.680 --> 00:04:32.720
or gender,

00:04:33.630 --> 00:04:34.670
what matters

00:04:35.260 --> 00:04:36.860
is the path one has traveled.

00:04:38.240 --> 00:04:39.500
Do you really think so?

00:04:40.040 --> 00:04:40.840
Yes.

00:04:42.320 --> 00:04:44.320
That's why I admire Your Highness so much.

00:04:44.320 --> 00:04:45.840
You're bold and spirited,

00:04:46.040 --> 00:04:48.250
never concerning yourself with status

00:04:48.280 --> 00:04:49.159
or hierarchy.

00:04:55.250 --> 00:04:56.100
I'm sorry.

00:04:57.740 --> 00:04:59.659
I'm the one who should apologize.

00:05:00.610 --> 00:05:01.440
What's wrong?

00:05:03.570 --> 00:05:04.640
I just feel

00:05:06.040 --> 00:05:08.200
that you and I are very compatible.

00:05:09.440 --> 00:05:11.900
I also feel a connection
with Your Highness,

00:05:12.340 --> 00:05:14.740
as if we've known each other
for a long time.

00:05:15.010 --> 00:05:16.130
But actually,

00:05:16.180 --> 00:05:19.510
Your Highness's way of doing things
is more similar to Xi's.

00:05:19.870 --> 00:05:21.600
It's just that Xi is still young

00:05:21.730 --> 00:05:24.390
and lacks
Your Highness's insight and courage.

00:05:25.920 --> 00:05:27.180
If back then I had

00:05:27.510 --> 00:05:29.440
been willing to remove my shackles

00:05:29.710 --> 00:05:32.110
and paid more attention
to those around me,

00:05:32.180 --> 00:05:33.090
perhaps

00:05:34.890 --> 00:05:37.550
the outcome
would have been different long ago.

00:05:44.850 --> 00:05:48.909
[Memorial Tablet of My Late Mother,
Madam Wang of the Zhou Family]

00:05:56.440 --> 00:05:57.840
Didn't Your Highness say

00:05:59.700 --> 00:06:01.090
you would protect us?

00:06:03.840 --> 00:06:05.660
Why did my mother still die?

00:06:10.310 --> 00:06:11.150
I'm sorry.

00:06:12.220 --> 00:06:14.400
Indeed, others cannot be trusted.

00:06:18.160 --> 00:06:20.280
I can only rely on myself.

00:06:24.860 --> 00:06:25.660
Xi.

00:06:25.760 --> 00:06:26.780
Xi!

00:06:28.110 --> 00:06:29.440
What are you going to do?

00:06:29.640 --> 00:06:31.920
Mother didn't die from illness.

00:06:33.640 --> 00:06:35.460
She was murdered.

00:06:44.840 --> 00:06:47.100
Why is this fragrance getting stronger?

00:06:47.820 --> 00:06:48.780
Could it be

00:06:49.250 --> 00:06:50.710
Mother died of poisoning?

00:06:52.320 --> 00:06:53.460
It was Madam Cui.

00:06:54.130 --> 00:06:56.670
Madam Cui killed her.

00:06:56.790 --> 00:06:58.140
I'm going to kill her.

00:06:58.159 --> 00:06:59.820
I will kill her!

00:06:59.840 --> 00:07:01.320
I must have revenge!

00:07:01.350 --> 00:07:02.150
Xi.

00:07:02.390 --> 00:07:03.190
Xi.

00:07:04.000 --> 00:07:05.430
Acting so rashly

00:07:05.840 --> 00:07:07.570
will only implicate yourself.

00:07:09.860 --> 00:07:11.790
Then what does Your Highness think

00:07:14.080 --> 00:07:15.800
I should do?

00:07:16.800 --> 00:07:18.520
I have arranged everything.

00:07:20.880 --> 00:07:21.960
Trust me.

00:07:26.300 --> 00:07:27.080
I will

00:07:29.940 --> 00:07:31.470
take this revenge with you.

00:07:34.740 --> 00:07:36.000
Why should I trust you?

00:07:47.700 --> 00:07:49.230
How could this be?

00:08:07.800 --> 00:08:08.890
Lieutenant Liang,

00:08:08.910 --> 00:08:09.870
show yourself.

00:08:14.860 --> 00:08:16.580
How did Your Highness know I was nearby?

00:08:16.580 --> 00:08:19.080
There are no such coincidences
in this world.

00:08:19.080 --> 00:08:21.170
That day when I saw
your master at the tavern,

00:08:21.170 --> 00:08:22.310
I realized

00:08:22.570 --> 00:08:24.550
he had placed spies around me.

00:08:24.680 --> 00:08:27.340
His Highness
is only concerned for your safety.

00:08:27.500 --> 00:08:29.290
Go tell your master

00:08:29.530 --> 00:08:30.920
to prepare a carriage.

00:08:30.940 --> 00:08:31.850
At midnight tonight,

00:08:31.850 --> 00:08:33.600
meet me at the back gate
of Zhou's Mansion.

00:08:33.600 --> 00:08:34.230
Yes.

00:08:38.179 --> 00:08:38.970
Your Highness.

00:08:38.970 --> 00:08:40.429
The princess arranged to meet at midnight.

00:08:40.429 --> 00:08:42.559
Do we really need to arrive this early?

00:08:42.909 --> 00:08:43.870
It's so late.

00:08:44.030 --> 00:08:45.650
Yet the princess still asked to meet me.

00:08:45.650 --> 00:08:47.580
What urgent matter could she have?

00:08:59.850 --> 00:09:00.710
Your Highness.

00:09:01.210 --> 00:09:02.010
Miss Ruoxi.

00:09:02.830 --> 00:09:03.870
I'm Fu Wei.

00:09:05.990 --> 00:09:06.790
Miss Ruoxi.

00:09:07.310 --> 00:09:08.030
Today,

00:09:08.050 --> 00:09:09.840
the princess requested this meeting.

00:09:09.840 --> 00:09:10.860
Please stop this nonsense...

00:09:10.860 --> 00:09:12.220
I really am Fu Wei.

00:09:14.600 --> 00:09:16.400
We've known each other for so long.

00:09:16.400 --> 00:09:18.160
How could I not recognize you?

00:09:22.330 --> 00:09:24.540
Gains, losses, glory and failure
are all determined by Heaven.

00:09:24.540 --> 00:09:26.140
The only thing a person can do

00:09:26.360 --> 00:09:28.090
is to strive for it on their own.

00:09:28.400 --> 00:09:29.930
Your Highness, do you think

00:09:30.010 --> 00:09:32.000
I'm someone who gives up easily?

00:09:35.740 --> 00:09:37.100
Do you believe me now?

00:09:38.410 --> 00:09:39.860
Xi and I are cousins.

00:09:39.950 --> 00:09:41.190
We look alike.

00:09:41.220 --> 00:09:42.880
What's so strange about that?

00:09:45.210 --> 00:09:45.890
Well,

00:09:46.510 --> 00:09:47.280
Princess,

00:09:48.280 --> 00:09:50.210
shall we get in the carriage first?

00:10:06.040 --> 00:10:09.840
I can't believe there're two people
in the world who look so similar.

00:10:14.500 --> 00:10:15.940
So where are we going now?

00:10:16.290 --> 00:10:17.750
The Wang family in Yuzhou.

00:10:20.720 --> 00:10:21.310
Hya!

00:10:51.580 --> 00:10:52.700
Your face...

00:10:54.680 --> 00:10:56.320
How is it identical to mine?

00:10:57.480 --> 00:10:58.440
I can't explain

00:10:58.710 --> 00:11:00.440
this matter clearly right now.

00:11:01.400 --> 00:11:02.640
But please trust me.

00:11:03.210 --> 00:11:05.080
I will go to Yuzhou
to investigate the loan sharking case

00:11:05.080 --> 00:11:06.480
and clear my aunt's name.

00:11:06.740 --> 00:11:07.850
During this time,

00:11:08.310 --> 00:11:10.790
you'll stay at Zhou's Mansion
using my identity

00:11:10.790 --> 00:11:12.030
to avoid suspicion.

00:11:16.880 --> 00:11:19.380
Though I look identical
to Princess Fu Wei,

00:11:20.780 --> 00:11:22.910
our fates couldn't be more different.

00:11:45.040 --> 00:11:45.840
Madam.

00:11:47.530 --> 00:11:49.790
I just saw Miss Ruoxi leaving the mansion

00:11:49.840 --> 00:11:51.500
and don't know where she went.

00:11:51.840 --> 00:11:53.100
Keep a close eye on her.

00:11:53.680 --> 00:11:54.810
You must be careful.

00:11:55.280 --> 00:11:56.360
If necessary,

00:11:56.740 --> 00:11:58.270
eliminate her completely.

00:11:58.970 --> 00:11:59.690
Yes.

00:12:00.140 --> 00:12:00.870
By the way...

00:12:02.140 --> 00:12:03.940
Watch the princess closely too.

00:12:04.460 --> 00:12:06.340
Report to me immediately

00:12:06.360 --> 00:12:07.890
if anything seems suspicious.

00:12:07.890 --> 00:12:08.650
Yes.

00:12:13.880 --> 00:12:15.080
Zhou Ruoxi.

00:12:17.150 --> 00:12:19.540
You want to avenge your mother?

00:12:22.120 --> 00:12:25.040
Soon you'll learn what it means

00:12:25.040 --> 00:12:27.300
to be an ant
trying to shake a mighty tree.

00:12:31.980 --> 00:12:34.530
[Wang's Mansion]

00:12:39.640 --> 00:12:42.260
News of the loan sharking case
has reached the Imperial City.

00:12:42.260 --> 00:12:44.440
The Wang family knows
they're under suspicion,

00:12:44.440 --> 00:12:46.510
yet they're making no attempt
to hide anything.

00:12:46.510 --> 00:12:48.510
Instead, their doors are wide open.

00:12:48.800 --> 00:12:50.120
Don't you think

00:12:50.800 --> 00:12:53.200
there's something suspicious about that?

00:12:57.220 --> 00:12:57.780
Look.

00:12:58.370 --> 00:13:00.620
That vendor
selling fried snacks by the door.

00:13:00.620 --> 00:13:02.440
Though his movements seem practiced,

00:13:02.440 --> 00:13:03.920
his apron

00:13:03.940 --> 00:13:05.740
doesn't have a single oil stain.

00:13:05.990 --> 00:13:07.260
And we've been sitting here

00:13:07.260 --> 00:13:08.540
for 10 minutes.

00:13:09.060 --> 00:13:10.860
He hasn't fried a single snack.

00:13:11.440 --> 00:13:12.160
Also,

00:13:12.460 --> 00:13:14.780
that vendor carrying vegetable baskets
and shouting

00:13:14.780 --> 00:13:17.340
has passed by the Wang family gate
three times already.

00:13:17.340 --> 00:13:18.220
So,

00:13:18.260 --> 00:13:20.390
while they appear open and welcoming,

00:13:20.870 --> 00:13:22.590
in reality, the surroundings

00:13:23.140 --> 00:13:24.340
are full of ambushes.

00:13:24.500 --> 00:13:25.420
In that case,

00:13:25.740 --> 00:13:27.350
the Wang family is definitely suspicious.

00:13:27.350 --> 00:13:29.080
Whether they're guilty or not,

00:13:29.480 --> 00:13:31.010
we'll find out soon enough.

00:13:32.540 --> 00:13:33.800
This tea is excellent.

00:13:33.930 --> 00:13:35.090
Try some.

00:13:41.970 --> 00:13:42.970
It's astringent.

00:13:45.640 --> 00:13:48.370
I used to find this tea
bitter and astringent too.

00:13:50.040 --> 00:13:51.900
But after drinking it for a while,

00:13:52.920 --> 00:13:55.050
I began to taste its sweet aftertaste.

00:13:55.360 --> 00:13:57.360
Many things can't be rushed.

00:13:58.240 --> 00:13:59.970
They need to be savored slowly.

00:14:07.500 --> 00:14:08.350
Madam.

00:14:14.920 --> 00:14:16.120
Your Highness.

00:14:19.260 --> 00:14:20.590
Mrs. Zhou, please rise.

00:14:21.040 --> 00:14:21.930
Yes.

00:14:23.370 --> 00:14:24.230
Your Highness,

00:14:24.400 --> 00:14:25.650
I have urgent matters,

00:14:25.650 --> 00:14:27.330
so I must take my leave.

00:14:32.650 --> 00:14:34.990
Since she thinks I'm Fu Wei,

00:14:35.720 --> 00:14:37.800
I'll use my identity as princess

00:14:38.100 --> 00:14:39.590
to teach her a lesson.

00:14:48.360 --> 00:14:49.820
The main gate is wide open,

00:14:50.110 --> 00:14:51.970
but the side door is tightly shut.

00:14:53.710 --> 00:14:55.110
It seems the Wang family

00:14:55.140 --> 00:14:57.200
truly has secrets they can't reveal.

00:14:59.450 --> 00:15:01.180
Since the door is sealed tight,

00:15:01.560 --> 00:15:03.890
how can we find out
what's really going on?

00:15:03.970 --> 00:15:06.010
The Wang family
all enter through the side door,

00:15:06.010 --> 00:15:06.780
and

00:15:07.520 --> 00:15:09.780
this position is closer to the main hall.

00:15:10.410 --> 00:15:11.490
Perhaps we can

00:15:11.910 --> 00:15:13.440
learn something from here.

00:15:14.880 --> 00:15:15.820
It seems you

00:15:15.850 --> 00:15:18.100
not only resemble
Miss Ruoxi in appearance,

00:15:18.100 --> 00:15:19.660
but also know everything

00:15:19.760 --> 00:15:21.890
about her maternal family's affairs.

00:15:33.640 --> 00:15:34.240
Hey!

00:15:34.290 --> 00:15:35.170
You two!

00:15:35.200 --> 00:15:37.800
What are you doing
sneaking around our gate?

00:15:40.020 --> 00:15:41.510
It seems your method

00:15:42.850 --> 00:15:43.650
won't work.

00:15:44.790 --> 00:15:45.590
Right now,

00:15:45.810 --> 00:15:47.050
what should we do?

00:15:56.310 --> 00:15:57.190
Hold me.

00:16:11.960 --> 00:16:13.230
I'm talking to you!

00:16:13.420 --> 00:16:14.750
What are you doing here?

00:16:28.670 --> 00:16:30.910
Oh, meeting your lover in secret.

00:16:32.490 --> 00:16:35.050
I thought you were thieves.

00:16:35.940 --> 00:16:36.940
Go away!

00:16:39.840 --> 00:16:40.720
Get going!

00:17:15.530 --> 00:17:16.440
Princess.

00:17:21.020 --> 00:17:22.750
Using someone and then discarding them

00:17:22.750 --> 00:17:23.880
is not a good habit.

00:17:44.250 --> 00:17:45.200
Now

00:17:45.780 --> 00:17:46.610
we're even.

00:18:20.680 --> 00:18:21.640
Continue.

00:18:22.240 --> 00:18:23.040
Madam,

00:18:23.210 --> 00:18:24.410
the princess is here.

00:18:34.860 --> 00:18:37.040
Your Highness, you've come unexpectedly.

00:18:37.040 --> 00:18:38.440
What brings you here?

00:18:38.540 --> 00:18:39.420
Kneel.

00:18:39.880 --> 00:18:41.590
Did I tell you to rise?

00:18:44.900 --> 00:18:47.540
My aunt's coffin
has now arrived in Daqing.

00:18:47.760 --> 00:18:49.520
But I thought it over.

00:18:49.920 --> 00:18:52.320
Lord Zhou and my aunt
were husband and wife.

00:18:52.390 --> 00:18:53.850
My aunt's memorial tablet

00:18:53.890 --> 00:18:55.720
should be placed
in the ancestral hall of Zhou's Mansion.

00:18:55.720 --> 00:18:56.640
Mrs. Zhou,

00:18:56.660 --> 00:18:57.660
what do you think?

00:19:00.220 --> 00:19:01.100
Well...

00:19:02.970 --> 00:19:04.880
This goes against proper etiquette.

00:19:04.880 --> 00:19:06.480
I cannot make this decision.

00:19:07.230 --> 00:19:08.310
I must

00:19:08.770 --> 00:19:09.830
consult with the master first.

00:19:09.830 --> 00:19:12.950
What if I insist
that you make this decision?

00:19:13.510 --> 00:19:14.310
I...

00:19:17.520 --> 00:19:20.880
I would still prefer
to wait for the master's return to decide.

00:19:20.880 --> 00:19:21.720
Mrs. Zhou,

00:19:22.050 --> 00:19:23.070
I want

00:19:23.290 --> 00:19:25.350
my aunt's memorial tablet

00:19:25.420 --> 00:19:28.280
placed in the Zhou's Mansion's
ancestral hall now.

00:19:29.260 --> 00:19:30.260
Madam Wang

00:19:30.290 --> 00:19:31.960
was only a concubine
in the Zhou's Mansion.

00:19:31.960 --> 00:19:33.350
I dare not rashly...

00:19:33.850 --> 00:19:34.800
-You...
-Madam.

00:19:35.040 --> 00:19:35.840
What?

00:19:36.210 --> 00:19:37.690
You dare to defy me?